0140/extras/524006d32f4d972d720ece13a43fb8a6.webm?t=1750970690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620140/extras/524006d32f4d972d720ece13a43fb8a6.mp4?t=1750970690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620140/extras/da46b4295388e1ae31ef399a88a0db0f.avif?t=1750970690\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620140/extras_big/da46b4295388e1ae31ef399a88a0db0f.avif?t=1750970690 width=800 height=640 /></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620140/extras/5a6932952e182e93ac8f8e0d5946dfff.poster.avif?t=1750970690\" width=600 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620140/extras/5a6932952e182e93ac8f8e0d5946dfff.webm?t=1750970690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620140/extras/5a6932952e182e93ac8f8e0d5946dfff.mp4?t=1750970690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>THEANTHRIA</strong>! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a furry dating simulator in progress in which you are the only human in existence! Humans in this world are seen as divine, almost mythical  creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your human-tier dexterity and intelligence make you a perfect fit for a DyNein Delivery Pilot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talk to the girls in town, get to know them, give them presents and have fun with them!</p><p class=\"bb_p